  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">In the <span class=\"italic \">xy</span>-plane, line <span class=\"italic\">k</span> is defined by <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x plus y equals 0\"></span></span>. Line <span class=\"italic\">j</span> is perpendicular to line <span class=\"italic\">k</span>, and the <span class=\"italic \">y</span>-intercept of line <span class=\"italic\">j</span> is <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"the point with coordinates 0 comma 3\"></span></span>. Which of the following is an equation of line <span class=\"italic \">j</span> ?</p>\n",
